  "title": "Electrical and Instrumentation Engineer (URGENT)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare Electrical and Instrumentation design documents including Lighting design and calculation.</li><li>Preparation of lighting layout 2D and 3D drawings, Lighting circuit diagram. Earthing and Lightning Protection design and drafting of layout, section, and elevation drawings.</li><li>Cable ladder, conduit, trunking, cable routing design. Preparation of 2D and 3D design drawings.</li><li>Cable sizing calculation, prepare Electrical cable schedule Prepare material take off (MTO) for material purchase.</li><li>Fire Alarm, CCTV, Card Access, Public Addressing system design, preparation of system schematic and Layout drawings 2D and 3D.</li><li>Preparation of Instrument Location layout drawing Preparation of Junction box termination drawings, Instrument Loop diagram Preparation of instrument Hook up, typical installation details.</li><li>Preparation of instrument cable schedule Design coordination with internal design disciplines such as Structure, mechanical, piping team for design interface issue.</li><li>Attend 3D model review and coordination with internal discipline engineers to resolves clashes.</li><li>Attend site survey and provide design sketches such as cable routing, support installation details, etc.</li><li>Support project tender team for material take-off from client tender documents.Attend factory inspection for E&I related material such as Fire alarm, CCTV, MCC, PLC system.</li><li>Support construction site to raise material purchase request, evaluation vendor quotation, preparation of Material approval submission.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree or Diploma in Electrical or Electronics Engineering.</li><li>3~5 Year of relevant design experiences</li><li><strong>Fresh graduates are welcome to apply</strong></li><li>Minimum hands-on experience for using design software such as AutoCAD MEP (Electrical), AutoCAD Plant 3D, Navisworks Manage, DIALux.</li><li>Support site testing & commissioning work such as fire alarm system, CCTV System, DCS loop check, etc.</li></ul><p></p>",
